[
    {
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 3.42,
        "text": "I sometimes wonder about the conversations your mom and dad have with you.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 3.48,
        "end": 5.2,
        "text": "Well, my mom, she loves it, right?",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": true
    },
    {
        "start": 5.22,
        "end": 10.2,
        "text": "Because obviously, like she invested 21 years of her life into making me who I am",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 10.2,
        "end": 13.26,
        "text": "and to raising me and, you know, I wasn't always the easiest to work with,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 13.26,
        "end": 13.94,
        "text": "especially when I was younger.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 13.98,
        "end": 16.32,
        "text": "I was very passionate about wanting to be a YouTuber.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 16.52,
        "end": 18.22,
        "text": "I mean, I don't even know how I would, but I was just kind of like,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 18.26,
        "end": 21.14,
        "text": "mom, I just want to be a YouTuber and get a degree, get a job, do this.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 21.38,
        "end": 25.16,
        "text": "Like they're two completely different worlds that were constantly worldviews,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 25.16,
        "end": 27.52,
        "text": "constantly clashing between me and my mom when we were younger.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 27.66,
        "end": 28.48,
        "text": "That was not easy.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 28.48,
        "end": 32.12,
        "text": "But, you know, as things started to work, she eventually came around to it.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 32.32,
        "end": 36.18,
        "text": "And when I got more money on a single brand deal one time than she was making",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 36.18,
        "end": 39.88,
        "text": "an entire year, that's when she was like, OK, I trust you, Jimmy.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 40.1,
        "end": 42.94,
        "text": "I believe you know what you're doing and you're going to figure it out.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 43.02,
        "end": 44.02,
        "text": "It's been completely different.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    }
]